Revision history for Dancer-Plugin-Thumbnail

0.16    2020-01-08
        * Fixed tests for new libgd versions again and again

0.15    2020-01-07
        * Fixed tests for new libgd versions again

0.14    2017-04-24
        * Fixed tests for new libgd versions

0.13    2016-08-15
        * Switched to JSON::MaybeXS (instead of JSON::Any)

0.12    2015-11-29
        * Added META.yml into distribution.

0.11    2015-10-30
        * Removed MYMETA.* from distribution.

0.10    2014-04-09
        * Adopted to pre 5.008
        * Fixed cunfusing comment
        * Fixed tests for some libgd versions

0.09    2014-03-24
        * Bump version.

0.08    2014-03-24
        * Removed 'experimental' features ('smartmatch' and 'switch').

0.07    2011-09-05
        * Removed annoying debug message.

0.06    2011-08-09
        * Required Dancer version set to 1.3071
          (&Dancer::FileUtils::path was fixed).

0.05    2011-07-12
        * t/05-format.t fixed for 'gif size'
        * Required Dancer version set to 1.3030
          (&Dancer::Test::response_headers_include was implemented).

0.04    2011-07-11
        * Tests enhancements.

0.03    2011-07-10
        * POD fixes.
        * Tests enhancements.

0.02    2011-07-08
        * Aliases (shortcuts) for operation arguments.
        * POD fixes.

0.01    2011-07-07
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

